REQUIREMENTS
------------
1. The utility needs bash not sh. So make sure you have bash installed. 


INSTALL
-------
1. Copy the a2makestie file to ~/bin if ~/bin is added to your path.
   Otherwise just copy it to /usr/local/sbin/ or /usr/sbin/
   
2. Make it executable (chmod +x)

3. Now you are ready to use it



CONFIGURATION
-------------
To configure it open the file using text editor. Read the comments and changes the values if necessary.

